---
title: Middle Eastern Salmon & Veggie Couscous with Lemon Yoghurt & Parsley
description: Can’t decide between sweet or savoury, don’t worry we couldn’t either so we combined it into one! Tender salmon is cooked in our Middle Eastern seasoning and then glazed in a layer of honey. You won’t have to worry about picking one flavour over the other again with this recipe under your belt.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
